\id 1TI - Akawaio New Testament Translation Project 
\h 1 TEMU'TI 
\toc1 Wapiyaro' Kareta Paarʉ Nennoko'pʉ Temu'ti Ena' 
\toc2 1 Temu'ti 
\toc3 1 Temu'ti 
\mt2 Wapiyaro' Kareta Paarʉ Nennoko'pʉ 
\mt1 Temu'ti 
\mt2 Ena' 
\imt1 Ekamanin 
\ip Temu'ti, Kʉri'san moine Eisa Mʉre'pʉ winon esi'pʉ Esuwerʉ pon isan pe mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ikʉipʉnʉ esi'pʉ Kiri' pe. Paarʉ isakon pe mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ipika'tɨnin pe iyena'pʉ itekare ekamai' itɨto' tʉrawasooi yau. Wapiyaro' Paarʉ Nʉmenuka'pʉ Kareta usaurokʉ osorʉwawon eke ton ewankamanin pɨ'. 
\ip Imenukasa' kareta esi wapiya kuru panamanin pe so'si tau ennakanin enupan nɨto' namai'. Serɨ enupan nɨto', e'sumasa' Esuwerʉ amʉ' mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ Esuwerʉ amʉ' pen eseru pokon pe, tapurɨsen pɨ' iyesi serɨ ipun pe e'nɨto' yau orʉ esi ɨri pe, mɨrɨpan ka'pon uya tepika'tɨto' epoto' rɨken esi tekamasen pen i'tuto' iya winɨ, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ eseru ton winɨ tʉron nɨ ton kiyari namai' e'nɨto' mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ temari'mai' pʉra e'nɨto'. Imenukasa' kareta kanan esi enupan nɨto' en pe, so'si mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ Papa apurɨpɨ'to' esa' pe e'nɨto' pɨ', enpoika pokon pe so'si epuru ton mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ to' pika'tɨnin nan eseru e'to' pɨ'. Iu'matʉ pe, Temu'ti panamasa' wakʉ pe Sises Kʉrai poitorʉ pe mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ itʉrawasooi ton pɨ' ɨ'si'taino kon tamu'kuru' ke'ne te'san apurɨnin nan pɨ' iye'to' pɨ'. 
\iot Iyawon Ekamanin 
\io1 Ekamanin (1:1-2) 
\io1 Enupan nɨto' so'si mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ itʉrawasooi ku'nin nan pɨ' (1:3—3:16) 
\io1 Temu'ti enupato' itʉrawasooi pɨ' (4:1—6:21) 
\c 1  
\p  
\v 1 Paarʉ, Kʉrai Sises nennoko'pʉ tekareei ekamai' Papa uya tapiyo'mai' urɨ'nokon pika'tɨnin mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ Kʉrai Sises, urɨ'nokon e'ku'to' ipɨ' winɨpaino, 
\p  
\v 2 Temu'ti, i'nai rɨ umu pe te'sen apurɨto' yau enakan:\x - \xo 1:2 \xt Inkupʉ'pʉ 16:1\x* 
\p Wakʉ nonkasa', usentu'man nɨto' mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tʉusewankamai' pʉra e'nɨto' Papa, Ikʉipʉnʉ mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ Kʉrai Sises, uyepuru kon winon. 
\s1 Panaman Ennakanin Nan Main Pɨ' Enupanin Nan Pɨ' 
\p  
\v 3 Ikupʉ pa kuru kɨnyekama'potaine' kasa Ma'sitoniya pona utɨtaine' a'tai, E'pe'sas po e'kɨ, kamo ka'pon amʉ' apiyo'makɨ to' ereutato' pe ennakanin usenupan nɨto' pɨ' enupan pɨ' to' esi namai',  
\v 4 panton pɨ' rɨ mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tʉtamokori kon pɨ' rɨ te'tʉse to' esi namai'. Serɨ ton uya ɨ'seyaton pɨ' e'nɨ emapu'tɨ mɨrɨ, Papa tʉrawasooi kasa pʉra rɨ, apurɨto' winon.  
\v 5 Serɨ apiyontɨn nɨto' neporonʉ esi usi'nʉnkan nɨto', tʉuye'sen esuken itewan e'nɨ mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ wakʉ pe itewan e'nɨto' mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ i'nai rɨ apurɨto' winɨ.  
\v 6 Tʉron kon utɨsa' serɨ ton piyapai, mɨrɨpan kon era'tɨsa' se pe rɨ usauro'nɨto' ya'.  
\v 7 Main, Mosi' winon pɨ' enupanin nan pe e'pai to' esi, e'tane ɨ'rɨ pɨ' tʉusaurokʉ kon tukai' to' uya i'tu pʉra rɨ iyesi, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tenu kon yau esii'ma i'nairon tato' tʉuya'nokon ipɨ' i'tu to' uya pʉra rɨ iyesi. 
\p  
\v 8 I'tu'nokon main, Mosi' winon esi wakʉ pe iye'to' awɨrɨ apurɨ pe iyesi yau.  
\v 9 I'tu'nokon nɨ nɨrɨ main, Mosi' winon ekonekasa' esi ipokena' ton iwano' pe pen e'tane main i'kwɨ'nin nan mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ Papa pʉra tiwano' kon pe e'paino kon iwano' pe, Papa pʉnon kon mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tʉmakooikena' nan, wakʉ ton pen mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ itekare awon kon pen; kamoro tʉkʉipʉnʉ kon mɨrɨ pe pʉra tʉsan kon wɨnin nan iwano' pe, te'wɨsan iwano' pe,  
\v 10 tekumasan mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tʉwaraino kon a'kɨrɨ te'san, poitorʉ ton kʉrʉpo'pomanin nan mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ kasi ye' ton mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ i'nai rɨ usaurokʉ tai'ma kasi ye' ton iwano'—mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ɨ'rɨ rɨ ipoken pʉra na'ne' wakʉ usenupan nɨto' piyapai,  
\v 11 wakʉ Papa ekareei tʉnamasen awɨrɨ e'nɨto', uyena' intʉrʉ'pʉ. 
\s1 Itepuru Uya Wakʉ Nonkasa' Paarʉ Ena' 
\p  
\v 12 Tenki ta uya uyepuru kon Kʉrai Sises pɨ', umeruntɨrʉ ke urepasa' iya na'ne', tʉmaimu awɨron pe esi tukai' upɨ' isenuminkasa' pɨ', uyanʉnsa' iya tʉtʉrawasooi ya'.  
\v 13 Ɨri pe rɨ tʉpɨ' usauro'pɨ'sa' e'tane, tapurɨnin nan nɨ kota'masa' uya e'tane, ɨsɨ pe rɨ e'pɨ'sa' e'tane. E'tane rɨ, upɨ' isentu'ma'pʉ, apʉne pʉra i'tu uya pʉra iyesi uya mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ apurɨ uya pʉra rɨ iyesi uya iku'sa' wenai.\x - \xo 1:13 \xt Inkupʉ'pʉ 8:3; 9:4-5\x* 
\v 14 Wakʉ nonkasa' uyepuru kon uya e'tʉrʉ'pʉ upona eke pe rɨ, apurɨto' mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ usi'nʉnkan nɨto' pokon pe Kʉrai Sises yau'ne na'ne' ton. 
\p  
\v 15 Serɨ, serɨ tapurɨsen kuru main tanʉnsen kuru rɨ: Kʉrai Sises uyee'pʉ non pona tʉmakooikena' nan pika'tɨse'na—urɨ na'ne' to' maku'pɨ kuru.  
\v 16 E'tane mɨrɨ wenai kuru si upɨ' usentu'man nɨsa', urɨ si tʉmakooikena' nan maku'pɨ kuru si yau, Kʉrai Sises uya tʉpʉ'kʉ kenan pen nɨ tʉuseta'kai' pʉra te'to' enpoikato' pe kamoro tapurɨ ton kon mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ inke rɨ uko'man nɨto' epoton kon nenton pe.  
\v 17 Serɨ si kin inkero', teri'sen pen, tʉusensen pen, tikin nan nɨ Papa, iwano' pe inamato' mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ eke pe kuru iku'to' nesii, tɨwɨrɨ rɨ. Amen. 
\p  
\v 18 Mooi, Temu'ti, se iku'kɨ ta uya ɨpɨ' pu'kena' pe te'san usaurokʉ'pʉ ɨpɨ' awɨrɨ, ipɨkɨrɨ ɨwesi eto'to' pe wakʉ pe eto'nɨto' yau,  
\v 19 wakʉ pe apurɨto' pɨ' mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ wakʉ ɨyewan pɨ' tʉuta'sii'. Tʉron kon uya serɨ ton nurunpasa' man, mɨrɨpan kon uya apurɨto' tʉuya'nokon ma'tanʉ'sa'.  
\v 20 Mɨrɨpan kon tonpa pe na'ne' esi Aimeniyas mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ Arisanta, mɨrɨpan kon nonkasa' uya Se'tan\f + \fr 1:20 \fq Se'tan\ft —Makoi ese' isakon, \fq Papa eseru ewaruma'tɨnin \ft ta e'kwa pe.\f* ena', ɨri pe tʉusauro'sen pe Papa pɨ' to' esi namai' to' usenupato' pe. 
\c 2  
\s1 Apurɨpɨ'to' Pɨ' Iku'kɨ Ta 
\p  
\v 1 Tanporon wapiya ekama'po tanporon kon pona rɨ tʉusennasen pe, tʉwɨpʉremasen pe, ekama'ponin pe ɨwesi pa, tenki tawon pe tanporon kon ka'pon amʉ' pɨ'—  
\v 2 kin amʉ' pona mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tanporo kamo eke ton pona, tʉusewankamai' pʉra uko'man nɨto' kon pe mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tʉtʉi pe tanporon nɨ Papa pokon pe e'nɨto' mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ wakʉ pe e'nɨto' yau.  
\v 3 Serɨ serɨ wakʉ, Papa, upika'tɨnin kon pori'manin,  
\v 4 tanporo ka'pon amʉ' epika'tɨ i'sero' mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ i'nairon i'tunin nan pe tenasan pe.  
\v 5 Apʉne pʉra tikin nɨ Papa esi mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tikin nan iporo e'nɨto' Papa mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ka'pon amʉ' ka'sanawon, kʉrɨ rɨ ka'pon esi Kʉrai Sises,  
\v 6 tʉmɨrɨ pe iye'tʉsa' rʉ'pʉ tanporon kon ka'pon amʉ' epe' pe—isekamasa' rɨ iweyu pe te'sen a'tai rɨ.  
\v 7 Serɨ ku'nin pe rɨ anʉnsa' rʉ'pʉ urɨ main anin pe mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ itekare ekamai' enno'sa' pe—i'nairon ekama uya serɨ, kasi pe esi pen—mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ i'nai rɨ apurɨto' ti'saai pe e'to' pe Esuwerʉ amʉ' pen iwano' pe.\x - \xo 2:7 \xt 2 Temu'ti 1:11\x* 
\p  
\v 8 Mɨ yawɨron kon nɨ warawoti'si amʉ' uya wakʉ temiyatʉ kon anʉmʉ i'se esi ɨpʉreman pɨ', sakoro mɨrɨ pe pʉra e'sei'pɨ' nɨ a'kɨrɨ pʉra.  
\v 9 Uri'sami'si amʉ' nɨrɨ epontɨ i'se esi itenu entai pʉra, tapurɨsen ye' pe mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ wakʉ iteseru ye' pe, ika'pɨ'sa' ipʉrʉ'tɨsa' i'pai pe pʉra mɨrɨ pe pʉra korʉ mɨrɨ pe pʉra mokon mɨrɨ pe pʉra epe'kena' ipon pe pʉra,\x - \xo 2:9 \xt 1 Pi'ta 3:3\x* 
\v 10 e'tane wakʉ ku'nin pe, uri'sami'si amʉ' Papa apurɨpɨ'nin nan pe te'san e'to' e' pe. 
\p  
\v 11 Uri'sami'si amʉ' usenupato' pe iyesi e'pana esii'ma mɨrɨpan kon e'to' pe iyesi main awɨron kon pe.  
\v 12 Uri'san e'to' pe enupanin pe mɨrɨ pe pʉra warawo' entai eke pe ta uya pʉra man; e'pana iye'to' pe iyesi.  
\v 13 Apʉne pʉra Atan koneka'pʉ wapiya, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ I' nin si.\x - \xo 2:13 \xt Iseneses 2:7, 21-22\x* 
\v 14 Mɨrɨpan Atan ennakasa' pʉra iyesi; uri'san nin ennaka'pʉ mɨrɨ, mɨrɨpan ena'pʉ tʉmakooi ke.\x - \xo 2:14 \xt Iseneses 3:1-6\x* 
\v 15 E'tane uri'sami'si amʉ' epika'tɨto' oton\f + \fr 2:15 \fq epika'tɨto' oton; \ft mɨrɨ pe pʉra, \fq uto'panto' oton\f* to' umu'ta winɨ—apurɨto' yau to' esi yau, usi'nʉnkan nɨto' yau, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ wakʉ pe tiwano' kon pe, tʉuse'se'tɨto' kon ke. 
\c 3  
\s1 So'si Epuru Ton Pe Te'san Mɨrɨ Awonsi'kɨ To' O'non Kon 
\p  
\v 1 Serɨ serɨ tapurɨsen kuru main: Ɨnʉ' uya rɨ tewan tʉsa' pe iyesi yau tʉrawaso amʉ' epuru\f + \fr 3:1 \fq tʉrawaso amʉ' epuru, \ft mɨrɨ pe pʉra \fq opaserʉ, \ft mɨrɨ pe pʉra \fq pi'so', \ft Enkeri'si pe. Kiri' maimu yau tʉponarɨ'ne mɨrɨ ta e'kwa pe iyesi tato' ton esi, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tʉponaron kon Kʉri'san amʉ' so'sii ton esi tʉponarɨ'ne iteseru, pʉse rɨ warai itepuru tʉrawasooi pɨ'.\f* pe, eke rɨ tʉrawaso i'se iyesi mɨrɨ.  
\v 2 Pʉse rɨ si so'si epuru e'to' pe iyesi isapemato' ipɨkɨrɨ pʉra, tikin nan nɨ tʉno'pʉ taan'pʉ pe, mentaino ye' pe pʉra, tiwano' pe tʉuse'se'tɨsen pe, tʉnamasen ye' pe, wakʉ pe ka'pon amʉ' ku'nin pe tiwʉ' tau, enupanin pe,  
\v 3 e'taripan nɨto' ya' iye'tʉsa' pe pʉra, ɨsɨ ye' pe pʉra e'tane ɨ'sɨ'mʉn yaino ye' pe, ɨsipɨkɨ'ne' e' pe pʉra, pʉrata i'nʉnkanin ye' pe pʉra.  
\v 4 Wakʉ pe tamʉtʉ ton esa' e' pe iye'to' pe iyesi mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tʉmunkɨ amʉ' esi tʉmaimu awɨrɨ ennin pe tʉnamai'ma wakʉ pe.  
\v 5 (Ɨnʉ' rɨ esi yau tamʉtʉ ton esa' pe e'nɨto' i'tu iya pʉra, nai kasa ken Papa so'sii mainanpa iya?)  
\v 6 Emen nɨ iyekonekasa' pe kʉse'nin, mɨrɨ pe iyesi a'tai, itaperʉka esi, mɨrɨpan uta'mo'ka mɨrɨ rɨ eseru aimenkato' o'koi' makoi kasa.  
\v 7 Wakʉ ku'nin ye' pe iye'to' pe iyesi itekare awon kon pen koro'tau, piyɨ'nʉ'nin ya' ita'mo'ka namai' mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ Makoi mareei ya'.\x - \xo 3:7 \xt Tai'tas 1:6-9\x* 
\p  
\v 8 So'si epuru pika'tɨnin nan,\f + \fr 3:8 \fq So'si epuru pika'tɨnin nan, \ft mɨrɨ pe pʉra \fq ti'kan, \ft Enkeri'si pe. Kiri' maimu yau tʉponarɨ'ne mɨrɨ ta e'kwa pe iyesi tato' ton esi, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tʉponaron kon Kʉri'san amʉ' so'sii ton esi tʉponarɨ'ne iteseru, pʉse rɨ warai itepuru tʉrawasooi pɨ'.\f* e'to' pe iyesi mɨrɨ kasa rɨ marɨ tʉnamasan ye' pe, i'nairon kon pe, mentai rɨ waain pɨ' te'san pe pʉra, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ wakʉ pe pʉra rɨ te'se pʉrata eponin nan pe pʉra.  
\v 9 To' uta'sito' pe ipan nɨ i'nairon ton apurɨto' pɨ' wakʉ pe itewan.  
\v 10 Wapiya to' i'tuto' pe iyesi; mɨrɨ a'tai nin si ɨ'rɨ pe pʉra rɨ to' esi yau, tɨwɨ si to' ne'tʉrawasomai so'si epuru pika'tɨnin nan pe. 
\p  
\v 11 Mɨrɨ kasa rɨ marɨ, to' no'pʉ ton\f + \fr 3:11 \fq to' no'pʉ ton; \ft mɨrɨ pe pʉra, \fq pika'tɨnin nan uri'sami'si amʉ'\f* e'to' pe iyesi, uri'sami'si amʉ' tʉnamasan ye' ton pe, ɨri pe rɨ tʉusauro'san ye' pe pʉra e'tane mentaino kon pe pʉra mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tanporon yau rɨ tapurɨsan ye' ton pe. 
\p  
\v 12 So'si epuru pika'tɨnin e'to' pe iyesi tikin nan nɨ tʉno'pʉ taan'pʉ pe, mɨrɨpan e'to' pe iyesi wakʉ pe tʉmunkɨ ton mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tiwʉ' tawon kon esa' pe.  
\v 13 Kamoro wakʉ pe iye'tʉrawasomasa' kon uya wakʉ yau rɨ e'nɨto' eporo mɨrɨ, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ eke rɨ Kʉrai Sises apurɨto' tʉuya'nokon yau to' usewankamato' pʉra rɨ iyesi. 
\p  
\v 14 Serɨ pe'ne rɨ ɨpiya' utɨ tukai' e'ku'tane, serɨ ɨnkupʉnʉ pe te'sen menuka uya,  
\v 15 uko'mamʉ pe iyesi yau, i'tu pa ka'pon amʉ' uya tiwano' kon pe tʉuko'manto' kon eseru kupʉ Papa iwʉ' tau, nurɨnan Papa so'sii pe na'ne', i'nairon ipiyaino mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ iyapon pe te'sen.  
\v 16 A'toma entai rɨ, Papa apurɨ pɨ' e'nɨto' onansa' pe iye'sa' rʉ'pʉ esi eke pe rɨ: 
\q1 Tʉpun ke\f + \fr 3:16 \fq Tʉpun ke; \ft mɨrɨ pe pʉra, \fq Ka'pon pe\f* isenpoika'pʉ,\f + \fr 3:16 \fq isenpoika'pʉ; \ft mɨrɨ pe pʉra, \fq Papa usenpoika'pʉ\f* 
\q2 Iya'kwarʉ uya enpoika'pʉ ipokena' pe, 
\q1 Inserʉ amʉ' uya ene'pʉ, 
\q2 Itekareei usekama'pʉ tʉpataron kon koro'tau, 
\q1 Itapurɨ'pʉ non po, 
\q2 Itanʉmʉ'pʉ a'kwa yau. 
\c 4  
\s1 Temu'ti Nʉku'ton Ekama 
\p  
\v 1 Wakʉ pe kuru rɨ Iya'kwarʉ uya ta, emennʉ'pʉ po rɨ tʉron kon uya apurɨto' nonkato' oton, mɨrɨpan kon utɨto' oton enku'tɨnin a'kwarʉ ton mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ makoi uya enupan nɨto' pɨkɨrɨ.  
\v 2 Mɨrɨ waraino usenupan nɨto' uyepʉ wakʉ pe te'ku'san kasi ye' ton poro, itewan iye'pusa' kon a'ne' wa'ka pun ke kasa wakʉ kupʉ i'tunin nan pen nɨ.  
\v 3 Ka'pon amʉ' emari'ma namai' to' kupʉ to' uya, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tʉron nɨ ton kiyari piyapai to' e'to' pe to' panama to' uya, Papa nʉkaa'pʉ tenki tai'ma kamoro apurɨnin nan mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ i'nairon i'tunin nan nanʉmʉnʉ rɨ.  
\v 4 Apʉne pʉra tanporon Papa nʉkaa'pʉ esi wakʉ pe, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ɨ'rɨ pʉra rɨ iyesi tʉnurunpasen pe tenki tai'ma anʉmʉ pe iyesi yau,  
\v 5 apʉne pʉra ipʉremasa' pe iyesi Papa maimu ke mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ɨpʉreman nɨto' ke. 
\p  
\v 6 Serɨ ton enpoika auya pe iyesi yau utonpa kon ena', wakʉ pe kuru Kʉrai Sises poitorʉ pe ɨwesi mɨrɨ, isemo'kasa' pe i'nairon ton apurɨto' yau mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ wakʉ enupan nɨto' iyawɨrɨ ɨwe'sa' na'ne'.  
\v 7 Ennakan nɨto' rɨ Papa pʉn nɨ panton pɨ' kesii mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ sepan nɨ panton no'sami'si' rɨ te'sen; e'tane ru'ku, Papa uya tasa' kasa pɨ' ɨsenupa'.  
\v 8 Apʉne pʉra pun enupato' esi tepe'pʉ ke mara rɨ, e'tane Papa pokon pe e'nɨto' epe'pʉ esi tanporo kuru rɨ nin, asa'rɨ rɨ te'ku'ton a'si iya serɨ pe uko'man nɨto' mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ serɨ enta' uko'man nɨto'. 
\p  
\v 9 Serɨ serɨ tapurɨsen kuru main tanʉnsen kuru rɨ  
\v 10 (mɨrɨpan pɨ' e'tʉrawasoman sa'man pe): E'ku'nɨto' tʉsa' nurɨnan Papa yau, tanporon kon ka'pon amʉ' pika'tɨnin, kamoro kuru sa'ne apurɨnin nan. 
\p  
\v 11 Serɨ ton e'ku'to' pe ka'kɨ mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ serɨ ton ke to' enupakɨ.  
\v 12 Tenu yau pʉra rɨ ɨnʉ' rɨ ɨku'nin mʉre' ɨwesi pɨ', e'tane apurɨnin nan nenton ɨnku'kɨ ausaurokʉ yau, ɨuko'manto' yau, ɨusi'nʉnkato' yau, apurɨto' auya yau mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ wakʉ pe esuken ɨwe'to' yau.  
\v 13 Uyepʉ pʉ'kʉ pona, e'tʉkɨ iye'menukasa' itekare ekamanin pe so'si tau, itekare ekamanin pe mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ enupan nɨto' ku'nin pe.  
\v 14 Ɨrepa'pʉ kʉseno'mai, ɨyena' itʉsa' pu'kena' maimu poro itepuru ton uya temiyatʉ kon nonkasa' a'taino rʉ'pʉ ɨpona. 
\p  
\v 15 Serɨ ton ti'tui' e'kɨ; tanporo te'tʉse e'kɨ ipona, tanporon kon uya ɨnkupʉnʉ ento' pe.  
\v 16 Ɨuko'manto' mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ enupan nɨto' auya enkɨ a'ko pe. Ɨnku'pai kuru e'kɨ, apʉne pʉra iku'sa' auya yau, asa'rɨ ɨyepika'tɨ kon, ɨmɨrɨ rɨ mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ kamoro ɨyetanin nan. 
\c 5  
\s1 Itaan'pʉ Ima'tasa' Kon, Kɨɨyi' Amʉ', Apiyo' Ton Pɨ' Panaman 
\p  
\v 1 Ɨsɨ pe kɨɨyi' pɨ' ke'sɨ'mai, e'tane ipanamakɨ ɨkʉipʉnʉ pe iyesi kasa rɨ. Moine ton iku'kɨ ayakon non pe rɨ,  
\v 2 no'sami'si ton asanon pe, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ama'nomi'si ton iku'kɨ aparusi ton pe, ɨri pokon pe pʉra. 
\p  
\v 3 Kamoro itaan'pʉ ima'tasa' kon tekota'mai' kuru na'ne' nan ti'tui' e'kɨ.  
\v 4 E'tane itaan'pʉ ima'tasa' rʉ'pʉ esi yau tʉmunkɨ ke mɨrɨ pe pʉra tʉpayan ke, tɨwɨ pʉsamoro wapiya apurɨto' tʉuya'nokon enpoikai tamʉtʉ kon mainanpa tʉuya'nokon winɨ tʉsan kon mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tʉnonan kon e'makapʉ pe, serɨ esi pɨ' Papa pori'manin pe.  
\v 5 Itaan'pʉ ima'tasa' rʉ'pʉ ipan pe tekota'masen mɨrɨpan nonkasa' tikin sarɨ uya te'ku'to' tʉsa' Papa pɨ', mɨrɨpan uko'mamʉ ewarupɨ mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ wʉi kaisa rɨ ɨpʉreman pɨ' mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ Papa ekama'po pɨ' tʉpika'tɨto' pe iya.  
\v 6 E'tane itaan'pʉ ima'tasa' rʉ'pʉ esi yau utɨn pɨ' pori' pe tʉku'nin pɨkɨrɨ tukai', iyeri'ka'sa' pe rɨ iyesi mɨrɨ nurɨne rɨ iye'tane.  
\v 7 Serɨ ton to' nʉkupʉnʉ ke ka'pon amʉ' auro'kaka'kɨ rɨ nɨrɨ, ɨnʉ' rɨ esi namai' tʉpokonomasen pe.  
\v 8 Ɨnʉ' rɨ esi yau tʉtonpa ton mainanpanin pe pʉra, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ a'kopan kon kuru sa'ne iyamʉtʉ ton, apurɨto' tʉuya nonkasa' iya mɨrɨ mɨrɨpan esi ipan pe rɨ apurɨnin pen entai. 
\p  
\v 9 Ɨnʉ' rɨ itaan'pʉ ima'tasa' rʉ'pʉ ese' kʉse'tʉnin itaan'pʉ ima'tasa' kon koro'ta' 60 kaisa rɨ mɨrɨ pe pʉra mɨrɨ entai iwʉipiyaai iyesi a'tai rɨken, tʉusaurokʉ'pʉ tʉtaan'pʉ ya' awɨrɨ iye'sa' rʉ'pʉ,\f + \fr 5:9 \fq tʉusaurokʉ'pʉ tʉtaan'pʉ ya' awɨrɨ iye'sa' rʉ'pʉ; \ft mɨrɨ pe pʉra, \fq tikin nɨ itaan'pʉ e'sa' rʉ'pʉ\f* 
\v 10 wakʉ inkuu'pʉ pɨkɨrɨ ti'tusen, mʉre amʉ' emo'ka pɨ', wakʉ pe ka'pon amʉ' kupʉ pɨ', wakʉ ton pʉta korʉka pɨ', ekamʉn yau te'san pika'tɨ pɨ' mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ti'tui' pʉra rɨ wakʉ ton ku'nin pe iye'sa' rʉ'pʉ pe rɨken te'sen e'tʉrʉ. 
\p  
\v 11 Ama'nomi'si iwa ton itaan'pʉ ima'tasa' kon, to' kʉ'tʉrʉi mɨrɨ rupɨ ton asi' pona, apʉne pʉra i'se to' e'to' enasa' a'tai Kʉrai ena' to' e'tʉsa' entai, emari'mapai to' esi.  
\v 12 Mɨrɨ kasa nin si eseru aimenkato' nepʉ to' uya tʉpona'nokon, apʉne pʉra wapiya ikupʉ uya ta'pʉ tʉuya'nokon i'kwɨ'sa' to' uya.  
\v 13 Mɨrɨ rɨken pe pʉra, teseru kon pe to' uya iku'sa' enkurun nɨ mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ɨ'kwɨrɨ'pɨ' nɨ pɨ' ɨutɨ kaisarɨ'ne mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tenkurunsan pe rɨken to' enasa' pen, e'tane ka'pon pɨ' usauro'nɨ pɨ' rɨ nɨrɨ mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ manenpanin pe rɨ, tʉusauro'to' kon ye' pen nɨ pɨ' usauro'nɨ pɨ'.  
\v 14 Mɨrɨ wenai, ama'non ton itaan'pʉ ima'tasa' rʉ'pʉ ton emari'makapʉ i'se esi, to' umu'tato' pe, tiwʉ' kon nɨrɨ mainanpanin nan pe to' e'to' pe, uyeyaton kon usaurokʉ upɨ'nokon ɨri pe temapu'tɨi' pʉra.  
\v 15 Apʉne pʉra tʉron kon itaan'pʉ ima'tasa' rʉ'pʉ ton era'tɨka'sa' Se'tan\f + \fr 5:15 \fq Se'tan\ft —Makoi ese' isakon, \fq Papa eseru ewaruma'tɨnin \ft ta e'kwa pe.\f* pɨkɨrɨ tʉutɨsan pe. 
\p  
\v 16 Ɨnʉ' rɨ uri'san Sises apurɨnin pe te'sen tonpa ton pe, itaan'pʉ ima'tasa' rʉ'san esi yau, tɨwɨ to' pika'tɨi so'si pona e'tape'ne' e'nonka namai', so'si uya kamo itaan'pʉ ima'tasa' kon ipan pe kuru nekota'mayai'ne' nan pika'tɨto' pe. 
\p  
\v 17 Itepuru ton so'si eseru konekanin nan wakʉ pe esi mɨrɨ ɨsipona kuru tʉnamato' kon i'se, kamo kuru sa'ne itekare ekama pɨ' mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ enupan pɨ' te'tʉrawasomasan.  
\v 18 Apʉne pʉra imenukasa' itekare uya tasa', “Paka waraino mʉta kʉsemaikai inta yen ya' a'nai' are'kwa pe iwasa'pɨ'nin,”\f + \fr 5:18 \ft Isu'taronomi 25:4\f* mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ, “Te'tʉrawasomasen esi tepe'pʉ eponin ye' pe,”\f + \fr 5:18 \ft Ʉru' 10:7\f* tawon.  
\v 19 So'si epuru\f + \fr 5:19 \fq So'si epuru, \ft mɨrɨ pe pʉra \fq Erʉta, \ft mɨrɨ pe pʉra \fq Pʉrespi'ta, \ft Enkeri'si pe. Kiri' maimu yau tʉponarɨ'ne mɨrɨ ta e'kwa pe iyesi tato' ton esi, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tʉponaron kon Kʉri'san amʉ' so'sii ton esi tʉponarɨ'ne iteseru, pʉse rɨ warai itepuru tʉrawasooi pɨ'.\f* pɨ' usauro'nɨto' kʉsetai, asa'ron kon mɨrɨ pe pʉra osorʉwawon kon ennin nʉ'san esi a'tai rɨken metai'.\x - \xo 5:19 \xt Isu'taronomi 17:6; 19:15 \x* 
\v 20 Kamoro imakoitasa' kon esereme'kɨ annau, tʉron kon e'to' pe te'namasan pe. 
\p  
\v 21 Ayapiyontɨ uya serɨ, Papa uya mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ Kʉrai Sises uya mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ anʉnsa' kon inserʉ amʉ' uya entane, serɨ ton iku'kɨ, ukayai'ne' ton kupʉ auya i'se esi te'menkai' pʉra mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tenu yawon ke ɨwesi pɨ' kʉ'kupʉi. 
\p  
\v 22 Tʉusenutɨi' miya' tʉto' yau, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tʉron kon makooi yau rɨ kesii. Esuken nɨ e'kɨ. 
\p  
\v 23 Esuken tuna kʉsensii, e'tane mara rʉ'kwɨ waain anʉnkɨ ɨyewan epi' pe, inke rɨ takuru'ke te'sen pe ɨwesi pɨ'. 
\p  
\v 24 Tʉron kon ka'pon amʉ' makooi esi tense kuru rɨ, mɨrɨpan kon makooi utɨ to' rawɨrɨ utaimenkan nɨto' ya', e'tane tʉron kon makooi usenpoika emennʉ'pʉ.  
\v 25 Mɨrɨ kasa rɨ marɨ wakʉ kupʉ usene, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ wakʉ pe isene pʉra na'ne' uko'mamʉ pʉra rɨ iyesi te'so'nanse. 
\c 6  
\p  
\v 1 Tanporo apiyo' pe e'nɨto' pʉmʉkanto' ike o'no na'ne' nan e'to' pe iyesi ipan pe tesanon kon namanin nan pe, Papa ese' mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ina uya enupan nɨto' pɨ' ɨri pe tʉusauro'san esi namai'.  
\v 2 Kamo apurɨnin nan pe na'ne' itesanon uya mara to' namato' pe pʉra iyesi, apʉne pʉra ɨsitonpa pe tesi kon pɨ'. E'tane ru'ku, wakʉ pe parɨ to' apiyo' pe to' e'to' pe iyesi, apʉne pʉra to' tʉrawasooi rʉ'pʉ winɨ tepika'tɨsan pe apurɨnin nan esi pɨ', mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ to' esanon esi to' poitorʉ ton ni'nʉnkanʉ ton pe. Serɨ ton ke to' enupa' mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ to' uya iku'to' pe iku'kɨ. 
\s1 Pʉrata I'nʉnkato' 
\p  
\v 3 Ɨnʉ' uya rɨ ennakanin enupan nɨto' ke enupan yau mɨrɨpan esi wakʉ uyepuru kon Sises Kʉrai uya iku'tɨ' tasa' na'ne' mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ Papa uya tasa' kasa usenupan nɨto' pɨ' ewai' tawon pe pʉra,  
\v 4 esi mɨrɨ mɨ pe iye'ku'sa' pe mɨrɨpan uya ɨ'rɨ to'ka'nʉkʉ pʉra rɨ iyesi. E'ne' pe rɨ e'sei'pɨ'pai iye'to' uya ikupʉ mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ɨsipɨ' e'nɨto' main wenai. Mɨrɨ moron nʉ'pʉ pe ikinita, iyɨkɨnta, mɨrɨpan usaurokʉ ɨsɨ pe rɨ, ɨri pe tʉron kon esi tukai' isenuminka,  
\v 5 mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ miyarɨ rɨ e'sei'pɨ' nɨ pɨ' to' esi ɨri ke isenuminkato' ima'tasa' kon pokon pe, irapumasa' kon nɨ i'nairon pɨ' mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ pʉrata epoto' iwinɨ pe Papa uya tasa' kasa e'nɨ tukai' tʉusenuminkasan. 
\p  
\v 6 E'tane Papa apurɨ pɨ' e'nɨto' pori' pe esii'ma itesa' pe e'nɨto' pɨ' esi eke pe rɨ eposa' pe.  
\v 7 Apʉne pʉra ɨ'rɨ ne'sa' pʉra rɨ iyesi non pona, mɨrɨpan ɨ'rɨ arɨ pʉra rɨ iyesi iyapai.  
\v 8 E'tane ti'kiyari ke mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tʉpon ke e'nɨ pɨ', pori' pe rɨ ipɨ' e'nɨto' pe iyesi.  
\v 9 Ka'pon amʉ' ipʉrataaike' pe e'paino kon ena i'tupɨ'nɨto' mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ mare ya' mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tu'kan nɨ ɨri ton mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ɨsɨ ton i'se e'nɨto' ya' ka'pon ennasikanin ekota'man nɨto' mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ uma'tan nɨto' ya'.  
\v 10 Apʉne pʉra pʉrata i'nʉnka esi tanporo rɨ ɨri ton pʉrakon pe. Tʉron kon ka'pon amʉ' mentai pʉrata pɨ' te'san utɨsa' apurɨto' piyapai, mɨrɨpan kon uya tewan kon i'kwɨtʉ tu'kan nɨ pokoi ke. 
\s1 Temu'ti Apiyontɨ Paarʉ Uya 
\p  
\v 11 E'tane ɨmɨrɨ, Papa ese' pokon, tanporo serɨ ton piyapai ainʉnkɨ, ipoken e'nɨto' pɨkɨrɨ e'kɨ, Papa uya tasa' pɨ' e'nɨto' pɨkɨrɨ, apurɨto' pɨkɨrɨ, usi'nʉnkan nɨto' pɨkɨrɨ, imoronkato' pɨkɨrɨ mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ɨ'sɨ'mʉn yai e'nɨto' pɨkɨrɨ e'kɨ.  
\v 12 Eto'kɨ apurɨto' pɨ' ɨyetokʉ pe. Aka'nero' pe pʉra uko'man nɨto' pɨ' ata'sikɨ ɨkɨ'masa' na'ne' ya' wakʉ pe kuru mekamataine' tu'kan kon ennin nan koro'tau.  
\v 13 Papa enu yau, uko'man nɨto' tʉnin tanporon ena' rɨ, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ Kʉrai Sises, Ponsiyas Paire' rau tʉusekama a'tai wakʉ pe isekama'pʉ, ayapiyontɨ uya\x - \xo 6:13 \xt Isaan 18:37\x* 
\v 14 serɨ apiyontɨn nɨto' kupʉ pa ipara'paai pʉra mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ipokonomato' ipɨkɨrɨ pʉra uyepuru kon Sises Kʉrai usenpoika pʉ'kʉ pona rɨ.  
\v 15 Kʉrɨ rɨ kʉrɨ rɨ tʉweyu a'tai rɨ Papa nʉne'ton—Papa, wakʉ mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tikin nan nɨken esa' wannɨ, kin amʉ' kin mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ itepuru ton epuru,  
\v 16 kʉrɨ rɨ rɨken teri'sen pen mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ eporo pokena' pen nɨ a'kwa yau tʉuko'mansen, ɨnʉ' rɨ nene'pʉ pen nɨ mɨrɨ pe pʉra nenenʉ pen nɨ. Kʉrɨ rɨ iwano' pe inamato' mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ imeruntɨrʉ nesii, tɨwɨrɨ rɨ. Amen. 
\p  
\v 17 Kamo ipʉrataaike' pe te'san serɨ pe na'ne' non po apiyontɨkɨ mɨ pe te'ku'se pʉra mɨrɨ pe pʉra te'ku'to' kon tʉrʉ to' uya namai' tʉpʉrataai kon pɨ', apʉne pʉra tɨwɨrɨ rɨ moro te'sen pe pʉra rɨ iyesi; e'tane Papa pɨ' ru'ku nin te'ku'to' kon tʉto' pe to' uya, tanporon ke rɨ eke pe rɨ repanin pori' pe e'nɨto' pe.  
\v 18 Wakʉ ku'to' pe to' uya to' apiyontɨ', wakʉ to' nʉkupʉnʉ yau eke pe to' uya iku'to' pe, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ amʉre'mʉra to' e'to' pe ɨsekanpai te'sen ye' pe.  
\v 19 Serɨ kasa to' esi a'tai timamin kon amʉranʉkʉ to' uya mɨrɨ, meruntɨ pe te'sen iyapon pe nʉye'ai'ne' pata iwano' pe, to' uta'sito' pe uko'man nɨto' pɨ' i'nairon kuru si uko'man nɨto'. 
\p  
\v 20 Temu'ti, ɨyena' inonkasa' ene pa erasu pe e'kɨ. Papa uya tasa' pen nɨ pɨ' usauro'nɨto' mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ i'tunin pe e'nɨto' pɨ' e'sei'pɨ'nɨto' piyapai tera'tɨi' e'kɨ,  
\v 21 tʉron kon uya ekamasa' na'ne' mɨrɨpan kon utɨsa' apurɨto' piyapai. 
\p Tɨwɨ wakʉ nonkasa' nesii ɨpiyau'nokon.